UID:20260717-TWAFlight800explodesaftertakeofffromJFK3@nyc-calendar
DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260717
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260718
SUMMARY:TWA Flight 800 explodes after takeoff from JFK — 30th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:TWA Flight 800 exploded off Long Island shortly after leaving
  John F. Kennedy International Airport\, killing all 230 people aboard. 
 The investigation traced the cause to a center fuel-tank explosion and d
 rove lasting changes to aviation fuel-tank safety rules.\n\nhttps://www.
 ntsb.gov/investigations/AccidentReports/Reports/AAR0003.pdf
URL:https://www.ntsb.gov/investigations/AccidentReports/Reports/AAR0003.p
 df
CATEGORIES:anniversary
END:VEVENT
