DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260720
SUMMARY:World Cup final at MetLife Stadium
DESCRIPTION:3pm ET. The largest single sporting event ever hosted in the 
 New York region. Weeks of security\, transit and crowd planning converge
  on this day.\n\nhttps://nynjfwc26.com/schedule/
URL:https://nynjfwc26.com/schedule/
CATEGORIES:city-life
