DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260828
SUMMARY:The Battle of Long Island — 250th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:The Battle of Long Island on August 27\, 1776\, was the large
 st battle of the Revolution and a British victory that gave them New Yor
 k for the rest of the war.\n\nhttps://www.battlefields.org/learn/revolut
 ionary-war/battles/brooklyn
