DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260909
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260910
SUMMARY:FDNY ceremony for the 25th anniversary of 9/11
DESCRIPTION:The official Fire Department ceremony honoring the 343 member
 s killed on Sept. 11\, 2001 and the more than 400 who have since died of
  World Trade Center-related illness. Held at the Staten Island FerryHawk
 s' stadium as part of a year-long commemoration.
