DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260911
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260912
SUMMARY:9/11 attacks destroy the World Trade Center — 25th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:Al-Qaeda hijackers crashed two jetliners into the twin towers
  of the World Trade Center\, collapsing both and killing 2\,753 people i
 n New York City. It was the deadliest terrorist attack in U.S. history.\
 n\nhttps://www.911memorial.org/911-faqs
URL:https://www.911memorial.org/911-faqs
CATEGORIES:anniversary
END:VEVENT
