DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260918
SUMMARY:Chelsea bombing injures 29 — 10th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:A pressure-cooker bomb exploded on West 23rd Street in Chelse
 a\, injuring 29 people. Ahmad Khan Rahimi was arrested days later and se
 ntenced to life in prison.\n\nhttps://www.justice.gov/archives/opa/pr/ch
 elsea-bomber-ahmad-khan-rahimi-convicted-executing-september-2016-bombin
 g-new-york-city
