DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261106
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261107
SUMMARY:DC 37's contract expires
DESCRIPTION:The largest municipal union\, roughly 90\,000 workers. The ex
 piring 2021-2026 agreement sets the pattern for the teachers' union and 
 everyone else. The first major labor test of this administration.\n\nhtt
 ps://www.nyc.gov/assets/olr/downloads/pdf/collectivebargaining/2021-2026
 /dc-37-2021-2026-moa.pdf
