DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261116
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261117
SUMMARY:The fall of Fort Washington — 250th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:British and Hessian forces captured Fort Washington\, the las
 t American stronghold on Manhattan\, on November 16\, 1776.\n\nhttps://w
 ww.battlefields.org/learn/revolutionary-war/battles/fort-washington
URL:https://www.battlefields.org/learn/revolutionary-war/battles/fort-was
 hington
