DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261126
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261127
SUMMARY:The 100th Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade
DESCRIPTION:A milestone parade\; the count reaches 100 in 2026 because th
 e parade was suspended during the Second World War. A year-long celebrat
 ion campaign surrounds it.
