 nt headquarters in Manhattan after John D. Rockefeller Jr. donated $8.5 
 million to buy the East River tract.\n\nhttps://www.un.org/en/about-us/h
 istory-of-the-un
URL:https://www.un.org/en/about-us/history-of-the-un
CATEGORIES:anniversary
END:VEVENT
