DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270201
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270202
SUMMARY:State executive budget due
DESCRIPTION:In the year following a gubernatorial election\, the state co
 nstitution requires the governor's budget by Feb. 1. It determines city 
 tax authority\, transit funding and Medicaid cost-sharing — the single m
 ost consequential document of the Albany year.\n\nhttps://www.budget.ny.
 gov/
URL:https://www.budget.ny.gov/
CATEGORIES:money
END:VEVENT
