DTSTAMP:20260714T170654Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270704
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270705
SUMMARY:Slavery ends in New York State — 200th anniversary
DESCRIPTION:An 1817 law took full effect on July 4\, 1827\, ending legal 
